###############################################################################
# ChatModel vs ChatClient 비교 테스트
# 
# 이 파일은 ChatModel과 ChatClient의 차이점을 실제로 테스트할 수 있는
# HTTP 요청 모음입니다.
#
# 사용법:
# 1. Ollama 실행: ollama serve
# 2. 모델 다운로드: ollama pull gemma2:2b
# 3. 애플리케이션 실행: ./gradlew bootRun
# 4. IntelliJ/VSCode에서 각 요청 실행
###############################################################################

### 변수 설정
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

###############################################################################
# 1. ChatModel 기본 테스트
###############################################################################

### 1-1. ChatModel: 기본 질의응답
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatmodel/basic
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "What is Spring AI?"
}

### 1-2. ChatModel: System Message 포함
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatmodel/with-system
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "systemMessage": "You are a helpful assistant specialized in technology",
  "userMessage": "Explain microservices in simple terms"
}

### 1-3. ChatModel: 도메인 전문가
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatmodel/expert
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "domain": "Kotlin programming",
  "question": "What are the benefits of using coroutines?"
}

### 1-4. ChatModel: Entity 매핑 (수동 파싱)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatmodel/book-recommendation?genre=science fiction
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 1-5. ChatModel: 메타데이터 포함
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatmodel/with-metadata
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Explain the concept of dependency injection"
}

### 1-6. ChatModel: 스트리밍 응답
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chatmodel/stream?question=Write a short story about a robot

### 1-7. ChatModel: 대화 히스토리
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatmodel/conversation
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

[
  "What is the capital of France?",
  "What is the population of that city?",
  "What are some famous landmarks there?"
]

###############################################################################
# 2. ChatClient 기본 테스트
###############################################################################

### 2-1. ChatClient: 기본 질의응답
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/basic
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "What is Spring AI?"
}

### 2-2. ChatClient: System Message 포함
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/with-system
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "systemMessage": "You are a helpful assistant specialized in technology",
  "userMessage": "Explain microservices in simple terms"
}

### 2-3. ChatClient: 도메인 전문가
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/expert
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "domain": "Kotlin programming",
  "question": "What are the benefits of using coroutines?"
}

### 2-4. ChatClient: Entity 매핑 (자동 파싱)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/book-recommendation?genre=science fiction
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2-5. ChatClient: 메타데이터 포함
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/with-metadata
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Explain the concept of dependency injection"
}

### 2-6. ChatClient: 스트리밍 응답
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/stream?question=Write a short story about a robot

### 2-7. ChatClient: 템플릿 변수
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/translate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "text": "Hello, how are you?",
  "targetLanguage": "Korean"
}

### 2-8. ChatClient: 영화 추천
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/movie-recommendation?genre=thriller
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2-9. ChatClient: 제품 정보 추출
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/extract-product
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

"The new iPhone 15 Pro is a premium smartphone priced at $999. It features a titanium design, A17 Pro chip, advanced camera system with 5x optical zoom, and USB-C connectivity. Available in natural titanium, blue titanium, white titanium, and black titanium colors."

### 2-10. ChatClient: 여러 질문
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/multi-question
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

[
  "What is the capital of Japan?",
  "What is the population?",
  "What is it famous for?"
]

###############################################################################
# 3. 직접 비교 테스트
###############################################################################

### 3-1. 비교: ChatModel 기본
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/comparison/basic/chatmodel
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Explain REST API in one sentence"
}

### 3-2. 비교: ChatClient 기본
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/comparison/basic/chatclient
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Explain REST API in one sentence"
}

### 3-3. 비교: ChatModel System Message
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/comparison/system-message/chatmodel

### 3-4. 비교: ChatClient System Message
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/comparison/system-message/chatclient

### 3-5. 비교: 코드 복잡도 분석
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/comparison/complexity

### 3-6. 비교: 사용 권장사항
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/comparison/recommendations

###############################################################################
# 4. 성능 비교 테스트
###############################################################################

### 4-1. ChatModel 성능 테스트
# @name chatModelPerf
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/comparison/basic/chatmodel
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "What is 2+2?"
}

### 4-2. ChatClient 성능 테스트
# @name chatClientPerf
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/comparison/basic/chatclient
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "What is 2+2?"
}

###############################################################################
# 5. 에러 처리 테스트
###############################################################################

### 5-1. ChatModel: 빈 질문
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatmodel/basic
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": ""
}

### 5-2. ChatClient: 빈 질문
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatclient/basic
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": ""
}

###############################################################################
# 테스트 결과 분석 가이드
###############################################################################

# 1. 응답 시간 비교
#    - ChatModel과 ChatClient의 실행 시간은 거의 동일합니다
#    - ChatClient는 내부적으로 ChatModel을 사용하기 때문입니다
#
# 2. 코드 복잡도
#    - /api/comparison/complexity 엔드포인트 결과 확인
#    - ChatClient가 대부분의 시나리오에서 더 간결합니다
#
# 3. Entity 매핑
#    - ChatModel: 수동 JSON 파싱 필요 (ObjectMapper)
#    - ChatClient: 자동 변환 (.entity() 메서드)
#
# 4. 스트리밍
#    - ChatModel: Flux<ChatResponse>를 map으로 변환 필요
#    - ChatClient: Flux<String> 직접 반환
#
# 5. 사용 권장사항
#    - /api/comparison/recommendations 엔드포인트 결과 확인
#    - 일반적으로 ChatClient 사용 권장
#    - 복잡한 제어가 필요한 경우만 ChatModel 사용
